record.notes:
Hogan, David W. and Stephen W. Pattemore. 1988. Urak Lawoi': basic structures and a dictionary. Canberra: Pacific Linguistics.
Urak Lawoi' (meaning "men of the sea") is spoken by about 3,000 people on islands off the west coast of Thailand.
